com.facebook.litho.specmodels.generator

Class TypeSpecDataHolder

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.facebook.litho.specmodels.generator.TypeSpecDataHolder

  • public class TypeSpecDataHolder
extends java.lang.Object
    An object that holds data that can be used in the construction of a com.squareup.javapoet.TypeSpec.

    This is a wrapper that is used to allow TypeSpecs to be composed. It is a dumb wrapper - any checking of the semantics will be done in the TypeSpec itself.
